name: Wallet Bag In Lily-Print Dauphine Calfskin With Embroidery
description: Wallet bag in lily-print Dauphine calfskin embellished by 3D embroidery with painted resin and hand-applied crystal details. It features solid-color sides and placed embellishment that recreates the perfect symmetry of the design. Thanks to the detachable chain, it can be worn crossbody or carried as a handbag
size: 19.5 x 13 x 4 cm - 7.7 x 5.1 x 1.6 inches
